  <body dur="04:05.070">
    <div begin="00:18.880" end="04:05.070">
      <p begin="00:18.880" end="00:22.040" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:18.880" end="00:19.050">老</span><span begin="00:19.050" end="00:19.220">书</span><span begin="00:19.220" end="00:19.400">摊</span> <span begin="00:19.400" end="00:19.500">和</span><span begin="00:19.570" end="00:19.720">啤</span><span begin="00:19.720" end="00:19.830">酒</span><span begin="00:19.920" end="00:20.300">空</span><span begin="00:20.300" end="00:20.790">罐</span> <span begin="00:20.820" end="00:21.030">散</span><span begin="00:21.030" end="00:21.340">落</span><span begin="00:21.400" end="00:21.580">地</span><span begin="00:21.710" end="00:22.040">上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">老書攤 和啤酒空罐 散落地上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Old book stalls and empty beer cans scattered on the ground</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">古本屋台とビールの空き缶が 地面に散らばる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">낡은 책 가판대와 빈 맥주 캔이 바닥에 흩어져 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les vieux stands de livres et les canettes de bière vides s'éparpillent sur le sol</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Puestos de libros viejos y latas de cerveza vacías esparcidos en el suelo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein alter Bücherstand und leere Bierdosen liegen verstreut auf dem Boden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Banca de livros velhos e latas de cerveja vazias espalhadas pelo chão</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Старая книжная лавка и пустые пивные банки разбросаны по земле</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Vecchie bancarelle di libri e lattine vuote di birra sparse a terra</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">lao shu tan he pi jiu kong guan san luo di shang</span></p>
      <p begin="00:23.210" end="00:26.340" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:23.210" end="00:23.400">报</span><span begin="00:23.400" end="00:23.570">废</span><span begin="00:23.570" end="00:23.760">的</span><span begin="00:23.760" end="00:23.920">回</span><span begin="00:23.920" end="00:24.090">忆</span><span begin="00:24.090" end="00:24.300">在</span><span begin="00:24.300" end="00:24.480">路</span><span begin="00:24.640" end="00:25.210">旁</span> <span begin="00:25.210" end="00:25.350">有</span><span begin="00:25.350" end="00:25.480">了</span><span begin="00:25.690" end="00:26.080">锈</span><span begin="00:26.080" end="00:26.340">斑</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">報廢的回憶在路旁 有了鏽斑</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Scrapped memories by the roadside have gotten rust spots</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">廃棄された思い出は道端で 錆びついている</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">길가에 버려진 추억엔 녹이 슬었지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les souvenirs mis au rebut sur le bas-côté se couvrent de rouille</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Los recuerdos desechados junto al camino tienen manchas de óxido</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verfallene Erinnerungen am Straßenrand haben Rostflecken angesetzt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Memórias descartadas na beira da estrada ganharam manchas de ferrugem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Выброшенные воспоминания у обочины покрылись ржавчиной</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">I ricordi scartati ai margini della strada si sono arrugginiti</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">bao fei de hui yi zai lu pang you le xiu ban</span></p>
      <p begin="00:27.480" end="00:31.030" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:27.480" end="00:27.660">有</span><span begin="00:27.720" end="00:27.880">某</span><span begin="00:27.880" end="00:28.080">种</span><span begin="00:28.080" end="00:28.180">无</span><span begin="00:28.220" end="00:28.610">所</span><span begin="00:28.610" end="00:28.860">谓</span> <span begin="00:29.680" end="00:29.880">在</span><span begin="00:29.880" end="00:30.040">这</span><span begin="00:30.040" end="00:30.220">小</span><span begin="00:30.220" end="00:30.420">镇</span><span begin="00:30.420" end="00:30.750">弥</span><span begin="00:30.840" end="00:31.030">漫</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">有某種無所謂 在這小鎮瀰漫</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A certain kind of indifference permeates this small town</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">どこかどうでもいいような空気が この小さな町に漂う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어떤 무관심함이 이 작은 마을에 감돌아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Une sorte d'indifférence imprègne cette petite ville</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Una especie de indiferencia impregna este pequeño pueblo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Eine Art Gleichgültigkeit durchdringt diese kleine Stadt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Há um certo tipo de indiferença permeando esta pequena cidade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Какое-то безразличие витает в этом маленьком городке</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Una sorta di indifferenza permea questa cittadina</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">you mou zhong wu suo wei zai zhe xiao zhen mi man</span></p>
      <p begin="00:31.870" end="00:35.070" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:31.870" end="00:32.040">这</span><span begin="00:32.080" end="00:32.200">个</span><span begin="00:32.200" end="00:32.410">城</span><span begin="00:32.410" end="00:32.510">市</span><span begin="00:32.590" end="00:32.760">步</span><span begin="00:32.760" end="00:32.850">调</span> <span begin="00:32.900" end="00:33.320">是</span><span begin="00:33.320" end="00:33.530">如</span><span begin="00:33.590" end="00:33.980">此</span><span begin="00:34.020" end="00:34.180">的</span><span begin="00:34.400" end="00:34.750">缓</span><span begin="00:34.750" end="00:35.070">慢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這個城市步調 是如此的緩慢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The pace of this city is so slow</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">この街の歩みは これほどまでに穏やかだ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 도시의 발걸음은 이토록 느릿해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le rythme de cette ville est d'une telle lenteur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El ritmo de esta ciudad es tan lento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das Tempo dieser Stadt ist so furchtbar langsam</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O ritmo desta cidade é tão lento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ритм этого города такой неспешный</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il ritmo di questa città è così lento</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">zhe ge cheng shi bu diao shi ru ci de huan man</span></p>
      <p begin="00:36.240" end="00:39.360" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:36.240" end="00:36.400">霓</span><span begin="00:36.400" end="00:36.560">虹</span><span begin="00:36.560" end="00:36.650">灯</span><span begin="00:36.700" end="00:36.850">闪</span><span begin="00:36.890" end="00:37.090">烁</span><span begin="00:37.090" end="00:37.170">的</span><span begin="00:37.270" end="00:37.690">倒</span><span begin="00:37.690" end="00:38.200">影</span> <span begin="00:38.200" end="00:38.270">靠</span><span begin="00:38.350" end="00:38.670">在</span><span begin="00:38.720" end="00:39.050">窗</span><span begin="00:39.080" end="00:39.360">上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">霓虹燈閃爍的倒影 靠在窗上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The flickering reflection of neon lights leans against the window</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ネオンの瞬く影が 窓辺に寄り添う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">반짝이는 네온사인 불빛이 창문에 비치고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le reflet scintillant des néons s'appuie contre la vitre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El reflejo parpadeante de las luces de neón se apoya en la ventana</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die flackernden Spiegelungen der Neonlichter lehnen am Fenster</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O reflexo cintilante das luzes de neon encosta na janela</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мерцающее отражение неоновых огней ложится на окно</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il riflesso tremolante delle luci al neon si appoggia sulla finestra</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ni hong deng shan shuo de dao ying kao zai chuang shang</span></p>
      <p begin="00:40.510" end="00:44.060" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:40.510" end="00:40.730">错</span><span begin="00:40.730" end="00:40.820">过</span><span begin="00:40.910" end="00:41.090">美</span><span begin="00:41.090" end="00:41.170">好</span><span begin="00:41.260" end="00:41.430">的</span><span begin="00:41.430" end="00:41.520">那</span><span begin="00:41.600" end="00:41.980">时</span><span begin="00:41.980" end="00:42.510">光</span> <span begin="00:42.510" end="00:42.630">能</span><span begin="00:42.690" end="00:43.050">否</span><span begin="00:43.080" end="00:43.420">再</span><span begin="00:43.470" end="00:43.710">遇</span><span begin="00:43.770" end="00:44.060">上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">錯過美好的那時光 能否再遇上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Can the missed beautiful times be encountered again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">すれ違ったあの美しい時間に また巡り会えるだろうか</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">놓쳐버린 그 아름다운 시절을 다시 만날 수 있을까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ces beaux moments manqués pourrons-nous nous y recroiser ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Esos hermosos tiempos perdidos podré volver a encontrarlos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Können wir jene verpasste schöne Zeit wohl wiederfinden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Aquele belo tempo perdido será que podemos encontrar de novo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сможем ли мы вновь встретить то прекрасное упущенное время</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Potrò mai ritrovare quei bei momenti perduti</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">cuo guo mei hao de na shi guang neng fou zai yu shang</span></p>
      <p begin="00:44.860" end="00:48.340" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:44.860" end="00:45.060">老</span><span begin="00:45.060" end="00:45.190">旧</span><span begin="00:45.250" end="00:45.560">的</span><span begin="00:45.600" end="00:45.940">车</span><span begin="00:45.960" end="00:46.130">站</span> <span begin="00:47.040" end="00:47.230">空</span><span begin="00:47.230" end="00:47.420">旷</span><span begin="00:47.420" end="00:47.700">的</span><span begin="00:47.750" end="00:48.090">车</span><span begin="00:48.120" end="00:48.340">厢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">老舊的車站 空曠的車廂</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The old station and the empty carriage</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">古びた駅 がらんとした車両</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">낡고 오래된 역, 텅 빈 객차</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La vieille gare les wagons déserts</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La vieja estación los vagones vacíos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein alter Bahnhof und leere Waggons</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A velha estação os vagões vazios</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Старая станция пустой вагон</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La vecchia stazione le carrozze vuote</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">lao jiu de che zhan kong kuang de che xiang</span></p>
      <p begin="00:49.190" end="00:51.780" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:49.190" end="00:49.390">怀</span><span begin="00:49.400" end="00:49.540">念</span><span begin="00:49.560" end="00:49.750">从</span><span begin="00:49.750" end="00:49.920">前</span><span begin="00:49.920" end="00:50.050">的</span><span begin="00:50.090" end="00:50.300">人</span><span begin="00:50.300" end="00:50.630">来</span><span begin="00:50.690" end="00:51.020">人</span><span begin="00:51.020" end="00:51.780">往</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">懷念從前的人來人往</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Missing the bustling crowds from the past</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">昔の人の行き交う姿が懐かしい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">예전에 북적이던 사람들이 그리워져</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Nostalgique du va-et-vient des gens d'autrefois</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Extraño el ir y venir de la gente de antes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich vermisse das geschäftige Treiben von einst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sinto falta do vai e vem de pessoas de antigamente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Скучаю по суете людей что была раньше</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mi manca il viavai di persone di un tempo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">huai nian cong qian de ren lai ren wang</span></p>
      <p begin="00:53.530" end="00:56.950" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:53.530" end="00:53.770">招</span><span begin="00:53.770" end="00:53.830">牌</span><span begin="00:53.940" end="00:54.240">的</span><span begin="00:54.280" end="00:54.640">灯</span><span begin="00:54.640" end="00:54.820">泡</span> <span begin="00:55.690" end="00:55.870">在</span><span begin="00:55.870" end="00:56.080">夜</span><span begin="00:56.080" end="00:56.400">里</span><span begin="00:56.440" end="00:56.830">微</span><span begin="00:56.830" end="00:56.950">亮</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">招牌的燈泡 在夜裡微亮</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The signboard's lightbulb shines faintly in the night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">看板の電球が 夜の帳にほのかに灯る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">간판의 전구는 밤중에 희미하게 빛나고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les ampoules de l'enseigne brillent doucement dans la nuit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las bombillas del letrero brillan tenuemente en la noche</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Glühbirne des Schildes leuchtet schwach in der Nacht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">As lâmpadas do letreiro brilham fracamente na noite</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Лампочка на вывеске тускло светится в ночи</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le lampadine dell'insegna brillano debolmente nella notte</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">zhao pai de deng pao zai ye li wei liang</span></p>
      <p begin="00:57.870" end="01:01.160" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:57.870" end="00:58.040">过</span><span begin="00:58.070" end="00:58.170">去</span><span begin="00:58.250" end="00:58.520">的</span><span begin="00:58.620" end="00:58.820">背</span><span begin="00:58.960" end="00:59.270">包</span> <span begin="00:59.320" end="00:59.720">就</span><span begin="00:59.720" end="00:59.960">留</span><span begin="01:00.060" end="01:00.420">在</span><span begin="01:00.420" end="01:00.570">异</span><span begin="01:00.750" end="01:01.160">乡</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">過去的背包 就留在異鄉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The backpack of the past is left in a foreign land</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">過去のバックパックは 異郷に置いてきた</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">과거의 배낭은 타향에 남겨둔 채</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J'ai laissé mon sac à dos du passé dans cette terre étrangère</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La mochila del pasado se queda en una tierra extranjera</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Den Rucksack der Vergangenheit lasse ich in der Fremde zurück</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A mochila do passado fica na terra estrangeira</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Старый рюкзак так и остался на чужбине</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Lo zaino del passato è rimasto in una terra straniera</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">guo qu de bei bao jiu liu zai yi xiang</span></p>
      <p begin="01:02.060" end="01:07.260" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="01:02.060" end="01:02.160">于</span><span begin="01:02.210" end="01:02.620">是</span><span begin="01:02.620" end="01:02.810">我</span><span begin="01:02.920" end="01:03.150">决</span><span begin="01:03.310" end="01:03.670">定</span> <span begin="01:03.670" end="01:03.860">离</span><span begin="01:03.980" end="01:04.310">开</span><span begin="01:04.360" end="01:04.710">这</span><span begin="01:04.760" end="01:05.010">个</span><span begin="01:05.130" end="01:05.350">地</span><span begin="01:05.450" end="01:07.260">方</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">於是我決定 離開這個地方</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">So I decided to leave this place</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">だから僕は この場所を離れると決めた</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그래서 난 이 곳을 떠나기로 했어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Alors j'ai décidé de quitter cet endroit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Así que decidí irme de este lugar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Also beschließe ich diesen Ort zu verlassen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Então eu decidi sair deste lugar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Поэтому я решил покинуть это место</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Così ho deciso di lasciare questo posto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">yu shi wo jue ding li kai zhe ge di fang</span></p>
      <p begin="01:09.830" end="01:13.360" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="01:09.830" end="01:10.210">当</span><span begin="01:10.210" end="01:10.360">你</span><span begin="01:10.510" end="01:10.850">收</span><span begin="01:10.920" end="01:11.210">到</span><span begin="01:11.270" end="01:11.620">信</span> <span begin="01:11.620" end="01:11.820">我</span><span begin="01:11.950" end="01:12.300">还</span><span begin="01:12.340" end="01:12.720">在</span><span begin="01:12.720" end="01:13.100">流</span><span begin="01:13.100" end="01:13.360">浪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">當你收到信 我還在流浪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">When you receive the letter I am still wandering</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君が手紙を受け取る頃 僕はまだ彷徨っている</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네가 편지를 받을 때쯤, 난 여전히 방랑하고 있겠지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Quand tu recevras cette lettre j'errerai encore</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cuando recibas la carta yo todavía estaré vagando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn du diesen Brief erhältst wandere ich noch immer umher</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quando você receber a carta eu ainda estarei vagando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Когда ты получишь письмо я всё ещё буду странствовать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quando riceverai la lettera io starò ancora vagando</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">dang ni shou dao xin wo hai zai liu lang</span></p>
      <p begin="01:14.170" end="01:17.660" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="01:14.170" end="01:14.480">那</span><span begin="01:14.550" end="01:14.890">年</span><span begin="01:14.890" end="01:15.230">的</span><span begin="01:15.230" end="01:15.570">约</span><span begin="01:15.630" end="01:15.970">定</span> <span begin="01:15.970" end="01:16.170">都</span><span begin="01:16.280" end="01:16.660">放</span><span begin="01:16.690" end="01:16.890">在</span><span begin="01:17.010" end="01:17.340">心</span><span begin="01:17.390" end="01:17.660">上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那年的約定 都放在心上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The promise from that year is kept in my heart</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">あの年の約束は 全て心にしまってある</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그해의 약속은 모두 마음속에 간직하고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les promesses de cette année-là je les garde dans mon cœur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las promesas de aquel año las guardo todas en mi corazón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das Versprechen von damals trage ich tief im Herzen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A promessa daquele ano está toda guardada no coração</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Обещание того года всё ещё храню в сердце</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tengo ancora nel cuore la promessa di quell'anno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">na nian de yue ding dou fang zai xin shang</span></p>
      <p begin="01:18.450" end="01:22.340" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:18.450" end="01:18.800">随</span><span begin="01:18.850" end="01:19.220">身</span><span begin="01:19.220" end="01:19.290">的</span><span begin="01:19.360" end="01:19.490">照</span><span begin="01:19.560" end="01:19.930">片</span><span begin="01:19.930" end="01:20.150">里</span> <span begin="01:20.660" end="01:21.030">你</span><span begin="01:21.030" end="01:21.140">微</span><span begin="01:21.310" end="01:21.560">笑</span><span begin="01:21.560" end="01:21.640">的</span><span begin="01:21.750" end="01:22.110">模</span><span begin="01:22.110" end="01:22.340">样</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">隨身的照片裡 你微笑的模樣</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Your smiling face in the photo I carry with me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">持ち歩く写真の中の 君の微笑む姿</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">늘 지니고 다니는 사진 속 네가 웃는 모습</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dans la photo que je garde sur moi la douceur de ton sourire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En la foto que llevo conmigo tu forma de sonreír</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auf dem Foto das ich bei mir trage ist dein Lächeln zu sehen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Na foto que carrego comigo o jeito do seu sorriso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">На фотографии что всегда со мной твоя улыбка</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nella foto che porto con me c'è il tuo sorriso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">sui shen de zhao pian li ni wei xiao de mo yang</span></p>
      <p begin="01:22.800" end="01:26.740" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:22.800" end="01:23.190">亲</span><span begin="01:23.190" end="01:23.530">爱</span><span begin="01:23.560" end="01:23.830">的</span> <span begin="01:23.940" end="01:24.050">你</span><span begin="01:24.220" end="01:24.570">现</span><span begin="01:24.610" end="01:24.810">在</span><span begin="01:24.980" end="01:25.660">怎</span><span begin="01:25.710" end="01:26.100">么</span><span begin="01:26.100" end="01:26.740">样</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">親愛的 你現在怎麼樣</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">My dear how are you doing now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">親愛なる君よ 今はどうしているの</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 사랑, 넌 지금 어떻게 지내고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ma chérie comment vas-tu à présent ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Querida cómo estás tú ahora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mein Liebling wie geht es dir jetzt?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Querida como você está agora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Дорогая как ты сейчас</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mia cara come stai adesso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">qin ai de ni xian zai zen me yang</span></p>
      <p begin="01:27.160" end="01:30.640" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:27.160" end="01:27.530">当</span><span begin="01:27.530" end="01:27.640">你</span><span begin="01:27.850" end="01:28.230">收</span><span begin="01:28.250" end="01:28.560">到</span><span begin="01:28.610" end="01:28.960">信</span> <span begin="01:28.960" end="01:29.140">我</span><span begin="01:29.270" end="01:29.670">还</span><span begin="01:29.700" end="01:30.080">在</span><span begin="01:30.080" end="01:30.450">流</span><span begin="01:30.450" end="01:30.640">浪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">當你收到信 我還在流浪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">When you receive the letter I am still wandering</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君が手紙を受け取る頃 僕はまだ彷徨っている</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네가 편지를 받을 때쯤, 난 여전히 방랑하고 있겠지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Quand tu recevras cette lettre j'errerai encore</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cuando recibas la carta yo todavía estaré vagando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn du diesen Brief erhältst wandere ich noch immer umher</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quando você receber a carta eu ainda estarei vagando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Когда ты получишь письмо я всё ещё буду странствовать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quando riceverai la lettera io starò ancora vagando</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">dang ni shou dao xin wo hai zai liu lang</span></p>
      <p begin="01:31.440" end="01:35.010" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:31.440" end="01:31.850">想</span><span begin="01:31.850" end="01:32.110">起</span><span begin="01:32.200" end="01:32.510">牵</span><span begin="01:32.580" end="01:32.870">着</span><span begin="01:32.920" end="01:33.250">手</span> <span begin="01:33.290" end="01:33.600">走</span><span begin="01:33.660" end="01:34.060">过</span><span begin="01:34.060" end="01:34.220">的</span><span begin="01:34.350" end="01:34.670">小</span><span begin="01:34.740" end="01:35.010">巷</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">想起牽著手 走過的小巷</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Thinking of the alley we walked through holding hands</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">手を繋いで歩いた あの路地を思い出す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">손잡고 걸었던 작은 골목길이 떠올라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je repense à ces ruelles traversées main dans la main</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Recuerdo los callejones por los que caminamos tomados de la mano</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich erinnere mich an die Gassen durch die wir Hand in Hand gingen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Lembro do beco por onde andamos de mãos dadas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Вспоминаю переулок по которому мы гуляли держась за руки</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ricordo i vicoli attraversati tenendoci per mano</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">xiang qi qian zhe shou zou guo de xiao xiang</span></p>
      <p begin="01:35.880" end="01:39.660" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:35.880" end="01:36.190">我</span><span begin="01:36.190" end="01:36.570">依</span><span begin="01:36.570" end="01:36.880">然</span><span begin="01:36.910" end="01:37.270">记</span><span begin="01:37.300" end="01:37.490">得</span> <span begin="01:38.000" end="01:38.180">年</span><span begin="01:38.180" end="01:38.280">少</span><span begin="01:38.350" end="01:38.520">初</span><span begin="01:38.520" end="01:38.670">吻</span><span begin="01:38.720" end="01:38.900">的</span><span begin="01:38.900" end="01:38.950">那</span><span begin="01:39.070" end="01:39.340">教</span><span begin="01:39.430" end="01:39.660">堂</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我依然記得 年少初吻的那教堂</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I still remember the church of our youthful first kiss</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">まだ覚えている 若き日の初吻のあの教会を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어릴 적 첫 키스를 했던 그 성당을 여전히 기억해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je me souviens encore de l'église de notre premier baiser de jeunesse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aún recuerdo la iglesia de nuestro primer beso de juventud</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich erinnere mich noch immer an jene Kirche unseres ersten Kusses in der Jugend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu ainda me lembro daquela igreja do nosso primeiro beijo na juventude</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я всё ещё помню ту церковь нашего первого юношеского поцелуя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ricordo ancora la chiesa del nostro primo bacio di gioventù</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">wo yi ran ji de nian shao chu wen de na jiao tang</span></p>
      <p begin="01:40.130" end="01:46.280" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:40.130" end="01:40.570">还</span><span begin="01:40.570" end="01:40.950">有</span><span begin="01:40.950" end="01:41.070">一</span><span begin="01:41.220" end="01:41.560">起</span><span begin="01:41.640" end="01:41.990">画</span><span begin="01:41.990" end="01:42.200">爱</span><span begin="01:42.300" end="01:42.900">心</span> <span begin="01:43.430" end="01:43.750">的</span><span begin="01:43.820" end="01:44.120">那</span><span begin="01:44.160" end="01:44.390">道</span><span begin="01:44.480" end="01:46.280">墙</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">還有一起畫愛心 的那道牆</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">And the wall where we drew a heart together</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">そして一緒にハートを描いた あの壁のことも</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그리고 함께 하트를 그렸던 그 벽도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et de ce mur où nous avions dessiné un cœur ensemble</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y esa pared donde dibujamos un corazón juntos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und an jene Wand an der wir zusammen ein Herz malten</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E daquela parede onde desenhamos um coração juntos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И ту стену где мы вместе нарисовали сердце</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E quel muro dove abbiamo disegnato un cuore insieme</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">hai you yi qi hua ai xin de na dao qiang</span></p>
      <p begin="02:03.010" end="02:06.140" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="02:03.010" end="02:03.150">霓</span><span begin="02:03.150" end="02:03.340">虹</span><span begin="02:03.340" end="02:03.440">灯</span><span begin="02:03.480" end="02:03.650">闪</span><span begin="02:03.670" end="02:03.850">烁</span><span begin="02:03.850" end="02:03.940">的</span><span begin="02:04.030" end="02:04.430">倒</span><span begin="02:04.430" end="02:04.920">影</span> <span begin="02:04.970" end="02:05.040">靠</span><span begin="02:05.100" end="02:05.380">在</span><span begin="02:05.470" end="02:05.760">窗</span><span begin="02:05.800" end="02:06.140">上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">霓虹燈閃爍的倒影 靠在窗上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The flickering reflection of neon lights leans against the window</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ネオンの瞬く影が 窓辺に寄り添う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">반짝이는 네온사인 불빛이 창문에 비치고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le reflet scintillant des néons s'appuie contre la vitre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El reflejo parpadeante de las luces de neón se apoya en la ventana</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die flackernden Spiegelungen der Neonlichter lehnen am Fenster</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O reflexo cintilante das luzes de neon encosta na janela</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мерцающее отражение неоновых огней ложится на окно</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il riflesso tremolante delle luci al neon si appoggia sulla finestra</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ni hong deng shan shuo de dao ying kao zai chuang shang</span></p>
      <p begin="02:07.250" end="02:10.790" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="02:07.250" end="02:07.420">错</span><span begin="02:07.480" end="02:07.570">过</span><span begin="02:07.660" end="02:07.840">美</span><span begin="02:07.840" end="02:07.940">好</span><span begin="02:08.020" end="02:08.190">的</span><span begin="02:08.190" end="02:08.280">那</span><span begin="02:08.350" end="02:08.670">时</span><span begin="02:08.740" end="02:09.260">光</span> <span begin="02:09.300" end="02:09.400">能</span><span begin="02:09.440" end="02:09.780">否</span><span begin="02:09.830" end="02:10.120">再</span><span begin="02:10.180" end="02:10.430">遇</span><span begin="02:10.510" end="02:10.790">上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">錯過美好的那時光 能否再遇上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Can the missed beautiful times be encountered again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">すれ違ったあの美しい時間に また巡り会えるだろうか</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">놓쳐버린 그 아름다운 시절을 다시 만날 수 있을까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ces beaux moments manqués pourrons-nous nous y recroiser ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Esos hermosos tiempos perdidos podré volver a encontrarlos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Können wir jene verpasste schöne Zeit wohl wiederfinden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Aquele belo tempo perdido será que podemos encontrar de novo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сможем ли мы вновь встретить то прекрасное упущенное время</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Potrò mai ritrovare quei bei momenti perduti</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">cuo guo mei hao de na shi guang neng fou zai yu shang</span></p>
      <p begin="02:11.650" end="02:15.130" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="02:11.650" end="02:11.780">老</span><span begin="02:11.810" end="02:11.910">旧</span><span begin="02:11.990" end="02:12.260">的</span><span begin="02:12.320" end="02:12.670">车</span><span begin="02:12.700" end="02:13.020">站</span> <span begin="02:13.790" end="02:13.970">空</span><span begin="02:13.970" end="02:14.170">旷</span><span begin="02:14.170" end="02:14.390">的</span><span begin="02:14.480" end="02:14.820">车</span><span begin="02:14.850" end="02:15.130">厢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">老舊的車站 空曠的車廂</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The old station and the empty carriage</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">古びた駅 がらんとした車両</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">낡고 오래된 역, 텅 빈 객차</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La vieille gare les wagons déserts</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La vieja estación los vagones vacíos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein alter Bahnhof und leere Waggons</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A velha estação os vagões vazios</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Старая станция пустой вагон</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La vecchia stazione le carrozze vuote</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">lao jiu de che zhan kong kuang de che xiang</span></p>
      <p begin="02:15.950" end="02:18.480" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="02:15.950" end="02:16.150">怀</span><span begin="02:16.150" end="02:16.300">念</span><span begin="02:16.300" end="02:16.500">从</span><span begin="02:16.500" end="02:16.680">前</span><span begin="02:16.680" end="02:16.810">的</span><span begin="02:16.850" end="02:17.070">人</span><span begin="02:17.070" end="02:17.420">来</span><span begin="02:17.420" end="02:17.770">人</span><span begin="02:17.770" end="02:18.480">往</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">懷念從前的人來人往</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Missing the bustling crowds from the past</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">昔の人の行き交う姿が懐かしい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">예전에 북적이던 사람들이 그리워져</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Nostalgique du va-et-vient des gens d'autrefois</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Extraño el ir y venir de la gente de antes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich vermisse das geschäftige Treiben von einst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sinto falta do vai e vem de pessoas de antigamente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Скучаю по суете людей что была раньше</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mi manca il viavai di persone di un tempo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">huai nian cong qian de ren lai ren wang</span></p>
      <p begin="02:20.260" end="02:23.680" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="02:20.260" end="02:20.500">招</span><span begin="02:20.500" end="02:20.570">牌</span><span begin="02:20.680" end="02:21.010">的</span><span begin="02:21.010" end="02:21.370">灯</span><span begin="02:21.370" end="02:21.570">泡</span> <span begin="02:22.440" end="02:22.620">在</span><span begin="02:22.620" end="02:22.830">夜</span><span begin="02:22.830" end="02:23.140">里</span><span begin="02:23.180" end="02:23.580">微</span><span begin="02:23.580" end="02:23.680">亮</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">招牌的燈泡 在夜裡微亮</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The signboard's lightbulb shines faintly in the night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">看板の電球が 夜の帳にほのかに灯る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">간판의 전구는 밤중에 희미하게 빛나고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les ampoules de l'enseigne brillent doucement dans la nuit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las bombillas del letrero brillan tenuemente en la noche</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Glühbirne des Schildes leuchtet schwach in der Nacht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">As lâmpadas do letreiro brilham fracamente na noite</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Лампочка на вывеске тускло светится в ночи</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le lampadine dell'insegna brillano debolmente nella notte</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">zhao pai de deng pao zai ye li wei liang</span></p>
      <p begin="02:24.620" end="02:27.910" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="02:24.620" end="02:24.770">过</span><span begin="02:24.810" end="02:24.910">去</span><span begin="02:24.990" end="02:25.260">的</span><span begin="02:25.370" end="02:25.580">背</span><span begin="02:25.710" end="02:26.020">包</span> <span begin="02:26.070" end="02:26.470">就</span><span begin="02:26.470" end="02:26.710">留</span><span begin="02:26.810" end="02:27.170">在</span><span begin="02:27.170" end="02:27.310">异</span><span begin="02:27.500" end="02:27.910">乡</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">過去的背包 就留在異鄉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The backpack of the past is left in a foreign land</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">過去のバックパックは 異郷に置いてきた</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">과거의 배낭은 타향에 남겨둔 채</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J'ai laissé mon sac à dos du passé dans cette terre étrangère</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La mochila del pasado se queda en una tierra extranjera</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Den Rucksack der Vergangenheit lasse ich in der Fremde zurück</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A mochila do passado fica na terra estrangeira</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Старый рюкзак так и остался на чужбине</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Lo zaino del passato è rimasto in una terra straniera</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">guo qu de bei bao jiu liu zai yi xiang</span></p>
      <p begin="02:28.800" end="02:34.020" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="02:28.800" end="02:28.910">于</span><span begin="02:28.950" end="02:29.360">是</span><span begin="02:29.360" end="02:29.550">我</span><span begin="02:29.660" end="02:29.910">决</span><span begin="02:30.050" end="02:30.420">定</span> <span begin="02:30.420" end="02:30.610">离</span><span begin="02:30.720" end="02:31.060">开</span><span begin="02:31.100" end="02:31.460">这</span><span begin="02:31.500" end="02:31.760">个</span><span begin="02:31.870" end="02:32.120">地</span><span begin="02:32.190" end="02:34.020">方</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">於是我決定 離開這個地方</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">So I decided to leave this place</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">だから僕は この場所を離れると決めた</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그래서 난 이 곳을 떠나기로 했어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Alors j'ai décidé de quitter cet endroit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Así que decidí irme de este lugar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Also beschließe ich diesen Ort zu verlassen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Então eu decidi sair deste lugar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Поэтому я решил покинуть это место</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Così ho deciso di lasciare questo posto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">yu shi wo jue ding li kai zhe ge di fang</span></p>
      <p begin="02:36.570" end="02:40.080" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="02:36.570" end="02:36.950">当</span><span begin="02:36.950" end="02:37.080">你</span><span begin="02:37.250" end="02:37.620">收</span><span begin="02:37.690" end="02:37.970">到</span><span begin="02:38.010" end="02:38.370">信</span> <span begin="02:38.370" end="02:38.630">我</span><span begin="02:38.690" end="02:39.050">还</span><span begin="02:39.080" end="02:39.460">在</span><span begin="02:39.460" end="02:39.840">流</span><span begin="02:39.840" end="02:40.080">浪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">當你收到信 我還在流浪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">When you receive the letter I am still wandering</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君が手紙を受け取る頃 僕はまだ彷徨っている</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네가 편지를 받을 때쯤, 난 여전히 방랑하고 있겠지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Quand tu recevras cette lettre j'errerai encore</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cuando recibas la carta yo todavía estaré vagando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn du diesen Brief erhältst wandere ich noch immer umher</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quando você receber a carta eu ainda estarei vagando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Когда ты получишь письмо я всё ещё буду странствовать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quando riceverai la lettera io starò ancora vagando</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">dang ni shou dao xin wo hai zai liu lang</span></p>
      <p begin="02:40.890" end="02:44.410" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L28"><span begin="02:40.890" end="02:41.240">那</span><span begin="02:41.280" end="02:41.640">年</span><span begin="02:41.640" end="02:41.970">的</span><span begin="02:41.970" end="02:42.320">约</span><span begin="02:42.380" end="02:42.680">定</span> <span begin="02:42.720" end="02:42.920">都</span><span begin="02:43.020" end="02:43.400">放</span><span begin="02:43.430" end="02:43.620">在</span><span begin="02:43.750" end="02:44.070">心</span><span begin="02:44.120" end="02:44.410">上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那年的約定 都放在心上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The promise from that year is kept in my heart</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">あの年の約束は 全て心にしまってある</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그해의 약속은 모두 마음속에 간직하고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les promesses de cette année-là je les garde dans mon cœur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las promesas de aquel año las guardo todas en mi corazón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das Versprechen von damals trage ich tief im Herzen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A promessa daquele ano está toda guardada no coração</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Обещание того года всё ещё храню в сердце</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tengo ancora nel cuore la promessa di quell'anno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">na nian de yue ding dou fang zai xin shang</span></p>
      <p begin="02:45.190" end="02:49.090" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L29"><span begin="02:45.190" end="02:45.550">随</span><span begin="02:45.590" end="02:45.920">身</span><span begin="02:45.960" end="02:46.040">的</span><span begin="02:46.110" end="02:46.240">照</span><span begin="02:46.300" end="02:46.680">片</span><span begin="02:46.680" end="02:46.910">里</span> <span begin="02:47.400" end="02:47.770">你</span><span begin="02:47.770" end="02:47.880">微</span><span begin="02:48.050" end="02:48.290">笑</span><span begin="02:48.310" end="02:48.380">的</span><span begin="02:48.500" end="02:48.860">模</span><span begin="02:48.860" end="02:49.090">样</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">隨身的照片裡 你微笑的模樣</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Your smiling face in the photo I carry with me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">持ち歩く写真の中の 君の微笑む姿</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">늘 지니고 다니는 사진 속 네가 웃는 모습</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dans la photo que je garde sur moi la douceur de ton sourire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En la foto que llevo conmigo tu forma de sonreír</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auf dem Foto das ich bei mir trage ist dein Lächeln zu sehen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Na foto que carrego comigo o jeito do seu sorriso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">На фотографии что всегда со мной твоя улыбка</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nella foto che porto con me c'è il tuo sorriso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">sui shen de zhao pian li ni wei xiao de mo yang</span></p>
      <p begin="02:49.550" end="02:53.480" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L30"><span begin="02:49.550" end="02:49.940">亲</span><span begin="02:49.940" end="02:50.270">爱</span><span begin="02:50.310" end="02:50.580">的</span> <span begin="02:50.690" end="02:50.810">你</span><span begin="02:50.970" end="02:51.320">现</span><span begin="02:51.360" end="02:51.630">在</span><span begin="02:51.730" end="02:52.410">怎</span><span begin="02:52.460" end="02:52.860">么</span><span begin="02:52.860" end="02:53.480">样</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">親愛的 你現在怎麼樣</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">My dear how are you doing now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">親愛なる君よ 今はどうしているの</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 사랑, 넌 지금 어떻게 지내고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ma chérie comment vas-tu à présent ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Querida cómo estás tú ahora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mein Liebling wie geht es dir jetzt?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Querida como você está agora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Дорогая как ты сейчас</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mia cara come stai adesso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">qin ai de ni xian zai zen me yang</span></p>
      <p begin="02:53.920" end="02:57.400" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L31"><span begin="02:53.920" end="02:54.290">当</span><span begin="02:54.290" end="02:54.400">你</span><span begin="02:54.600" end="02:54.970">收</span><span begin="02:55.000" end="02:55.320">到</span><span begin="02:55.350" end="02:55.720">信</span> <span begin="02:55.720" end="02:55.940">我</span><span begin="02:56.030" end="02:56.420">还</span><span begin="02:56.460" end="02:56.840">在</span><span begin="02:56.840" end="02:57.200">流</span><span begin="02:57.200" end="02:57.400">浪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">當你收到信 我還在流浪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">When you receive the letter I am still wandering</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君が手紙を受け取る頃 僕はまだ彷徨っている</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네가 편지를 받을 때쯤, 난 여전히 방랑하고 있겠지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Quand tu recevras cette lettre j'errerai encore</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cuando recibas la carta yo todavía estaré vagando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn du diesen Brief erhältst wandere ich noch immer umher</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quando você receber a carta eu ainda estarei vagando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Когда ты получишь письмо я всё ещё буду странствовать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quando riceverai la lettera io starò ancora vagando</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">dang ni shou dao xin wo hai zai liu lang</span></p>
      <p begin="02:58.190" end="03:01.730" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L32"><span begin="02:58.190" end="02:58.590">想</span><span begin="02:58.610" end="02:58.840">起</span><span begin="02:58.940" end="02:59.290">牵</span><span begin="02:59.320" end="02:59.620">着</span><span begin="02:59.670" end="02:59.990">手</span> <span begin="03:00.040" end="03:00.350">走</span><span begin="03:00.410" end="03:00.810">过</span><span begin="03:00.810" end="03:00.970">的</span><span begin="03:01.110" end="03:01.420">小</span><span begin="03:01.490" end="03:01.730">巷</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">想起牽著手 走過的小巷</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Thinking of the alley we walked through holding hands</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">手を繋いで歩いた あの路地を思い出す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">손잡고 걸었던 작은 골목길이 떠올라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je repense à ces ruelles traversées main dans la main</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Recuerdo los callejones por los que caminamos tomados de la mano</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich erinnere mich an die Gassen durch die wir Hand in Hand gingen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Lembro do beco por onde andamos de mãos dadas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Вспоминаю переулок по которому мы гуляли держась за руки</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ricordo i vicoli attraversati tenendoci per mano</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">xiang qi qian zhe shou zou guo de xiao xiang</span></p>
      <p begin="03:02.620" end="03:06.420" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L33"><span begin="03:02.620" end="03:02.930">我</span><span begin="03:02.930" end="03:03.310">依</span><span begin="03:03.310" end="03:03.620">然</span><span begin="03:03.650" end="03:04.040">记</span><span begin="03:04.040" end="03:04.250">得</span> <span begin="03:04.750" end="03:04.920">年</span><span begin="03:04.920" end="03:05.020">少</span><span begin="03:05.100" end="03:05.260">初</span><span begin="03:05.260" end="03:05.470">吻</span><span begin="03:05.470" end="03:05.610">的</span><span begin="03:05.640" end="03:05.700">那</span><span begin="03:05.810" end="03:06.080">教</span><span begin="03:06.180" end="03:06.420">堂</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我依然記得 年少初吻的那教堂</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I still remember the church of our youthful first kiss</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">まだ覚えている 若き日の初吻のあの教会を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어릴 적 첫 키스를 했던 그 성당을 여전히 기억해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je me souviens encore de l'église de notre premier baiser de jeunesse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aún recuerdo la iglesia de nuestro primer beso de juventud</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich erinnere mich noch immer an jene Kirche unseres ersten Kusses in der Jugend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu ainda me lembro daquela igreja do nosso primeiro beijo na juventude</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я всё ещё помню ту церковь нашего первого юношеского поцелуя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ricordo ancora la chiesa del nostro primo bacio di gioventù</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">wo yi ran ji de nian shao chu wen de na jiao tang</span></p>
      <p begin="03:06.880" end="03:13.020" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L34"><span begin="03:06.880" end="03:07.310">还</span><span begin="03:07.310" end="03:07.690">有</span><span begin="03:07.690" end="03:07.810">一</span><span begin="03:07.950" end="03:08.280">起</span><span begin="03:08.380" end="03:08.740">画</span><span begin="03:08.740" end="03:08.940">爱</span><span begin="03:09.050" end="03:09.620">心</span> <span begin="03:10.180" end="03:10.500">的</span><span begin="03:10.570" end="03:10.870">那</span><span begin="03:10.920" end="03:11.140">道</span><span begin="03:11.220" end="03:13.020">墙</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">還有一起畫愛心 的那道牆</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">And the wall where we drew a heart together</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">そして一緒にハートを描いた あの壁のことも</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그리고 함께 하트를 그렸던 그 벽도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et de ce mur où nous avions dessiné un cœur ensemble</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y esa pared donde dibujamos un corazón juntos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und an jene Wand an der wir zusammen ein Herz malten</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E daquela parede onde desenhamos um coração juntos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И ту стену где мы вместе нарисовали сердце</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E quel muro dove abbiamo disegnato un cuore insieme</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">hai you yi qi hua ai xin de na dao qiang</span></p>
      <p begin="03:28.630" end="03:32.140" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L35"><span begin="03:28.630" end="03:29.010">当</span><span begin="03:29.010" end="03:29.140">你</span><span begin="03:29.310" end="03:29.650">收</span><span begin="03:29.720" end="03:30.000">到</span><span begin="03:30.070" end="03:30.420">信</span> <span begin="03:30.420" end="03:30.660">我</span><span begin="03:30.750" end="03:31.100">还</span><span begin="03:31.140" end="03:31.520">在</span><span begin="03:31.520" end="03:31.900">流</span><span begin="03:31.900" end="03:32.140">浪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">當你收到信 我還在流浪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">When you receive the letter I am still wandering</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君が手紙を受け取る頃 僕はまだ彷徨っている</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네가 편지를 받을 때쯤, 난 여전히 방랑하고 있겠지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Quand tu recevras cette lettre j'errerai encore</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cuando recibas la carta yo todavía estaré vagando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn du diesen Brief erhältst wandere ich noch immer umher</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quando você receber a carta eu ainda estarei vagando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Когда ты получишь письмо я всё ещё буду странствовать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quando riceverai la lettera io starò ancora vagando</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">dang ni shou dao xin wo hai zai liu lang</span></p>
      <p begin="03:32.960" end="03:36.460" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L36"><span begin="03:32.960" end="03:33.280">那</span><span begin="03:33.340" end="03:33.680">年</span><span begin="03:33.680" end="03:34.020">的</span><span begin="03:34.020" end="03:34.360">约</span><span begin="03:34.420" end="03:34.730">定</span> <span begin="03:34.760" end="03:34.970">都</span><span begin="03:35.070" end="03:35.450">放</span><span begin="03:35.480" end="03:35.670">在</span><span begin="03:35.800" end="03:36.130">心</span><span begin="03:36.180" end="03:36.460">上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那年的約定 都放在心上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The promise from that year is kept in my heart</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">あの年の約束は 全て心にしまってある</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그해의 약속은 모두 마음속에 간직하고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les promesses de cette année-là je les garde dans mon cœur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las promesas de aquel año las guardo todas en mi corazón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das Versprechen von damals trage ich tief im Herzen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A promessa daquele ano está toda guardada no coração</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Обещание того года всё ещё храню в сердце</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tengo ancora nel cuore la promessa di quell'anno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">na nian de yue ding dou fang zai xin shang</span></p>
      <p begin="03:37.240" end="03:41.130" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L37"><span begin="03:37.240" end="03:37.590">随</span><span begin="03:37.640" end="03:38.010">身</span><span begin="03:38.010" end="03:38.080">的</span><span begin="03:38.150" end="03:38.280">照</span><span begin="03:38.350" end="03:38.730">片</span><span begin="03:38.730" end="03:38.960">里</span> <span begin="03:39.450" end="03:39.820">你</span><span begin="03:39.820" end="03:39.940">微</span><span begin="03:40.100" end="03:40.350">笑</span><span begin="03:40.350" end="03:40.410">的</span><span begin="03:40.560" end="03:40.910">模</span><span begin="03:40.910" end="03:41.130">样</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">隨身的照片裡 你微笑的模樣</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Your smiling face in the photo I carry with me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">持ち歩く写真の中の 君の微笑む姿</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">늘 지니고 다니는 사진 속 네가 웃는 모습</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dans la photo que je garde sur moi la douceur de ton sourire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En la foto que llevo conmigo tu forma de sonreír</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auf dem Foto das ich bei mir trage ist dein Lächeln zu sehen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Na foto que carrego comigo o jeito do seu sorriso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">На фотографии что всегда со мной твоя улыбка</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nella foto che porto con me c'è il tuo sorriso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">sui shen de zhao pian li ni wei xiao de mo yang</span></p>
      <p begin="03:41.600" end="03:45.530" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L38"><span begin="03:41.600" end="03:41.990">亲</span><span begin="03:41.990" end="03:42.320">爱</span><span begin="03:42.360" end="03:42.640">的</span> <span begin="03:42.740" end="03:42.860">你</span><span begin="03:43.020" end="03:43.380">现</span><span begin="03:43.410" end="03:43.680">在</span><span begin="03:43.780" end="03:44.440">怎</span><span begin="03:44.510" end="03:44.900">么</span><span begin="03:44.900" end="03:45.530">样</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">親愛的 你現在怎麼樣</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">My dear how are you doing now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">親愛なる君よ 今はどうしているの</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 사랑, 넌 지금 어떻게 지내고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ma chérie comment vas-tu à présent ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Querida cómo estás tú ahora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mein Liebling wie geht es dir jetzt?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Querida como você está agora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Дорогая как ты сейчас</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mia cara come stai adesso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">qin ai de ni xian zai zen me yang</span></p>
      <p begin="03:45.960" end="03:49.450" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L39"><span begin="03:45.960" end="03:46.330">当</span><span begin="03:46.330" end="03:46.440">你</span><span begin="03:46.650" end="03:47.030">收</span><span begin="03:47.050" end="03:47.360">到</span><span begin="03:47.400" end="03:47.760">信</span> <span begin="03:47.760" end="03:48.020">我</span><span begin="03:48.070" end="03:48.450">还</span><span begin="03:48.500" end="03:48.870">在</span><span begin="03:48.870" end="03:49.250">流</span><span begin="03:49.250" end="03:49.450">浪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">當你收到信 我還在流浪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">When you receive the letter I am still wandering</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君が手紙を受け取る頃 僕はまだ彷徨っている</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네가 편지를 받을 때쯤, 난 여전히 방랑하고 있겠지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Quand tu recevras cette lettre j'errerai encore</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cuando recibas la carta yo todavía estaré vagando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn du diesen Brief erhältst wandere ich noch immer umher</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quando você receber a carta eu ainda estarei vagando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Когда ты получишь письмо я всё ещё буду странствовать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quando riceverai la lettera io starò ancora vagando</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">dang ni shou dao xin wo hai zai liu lang</span></p>
      <p begin="03:50.240" end="03:53.800" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L40"><span begin="03:50.240" end="03:50.630">想</span><span begin="03:50.650" end="03:50.900">起</span><span begin="03:51.000" end="03:51.350">牵</span><span begin="03:51.380" end="03:51.650">着</span><span begin="03:51.720" end="03:52.050">手</span> <span begin="03:52.090" end="03:52.420">走</span><span begin="03:52.460" end="03:52.860">过</span><span begin="03:52.860" end="03:53.020">的</span><span begin="03:53.150" end="03:53.470">小</span><span begin="03:53.540" end="03:53.800">巷</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">想起牽著手 走過的小巷</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Thinking of the alley we walked through holding hands</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">手を繋いで歩いた あの路地を思い出す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">손잡고 걸었던 작은 골목길이 떠올라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je repense à ces ruelles traversées main dans la main</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Recuerdo los callejones por los que caminamos tomados de la mano</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich erinnere mich an die Gassen durch die wir Hand in Hand gingen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Lembro do beco por onde andamos de mãos dadas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Вспоминаю переулок по которому мы гуляли держась за руки</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ricordo i vicoli attraversati tenendoci per mano</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">xiang qi qian zhe shou zou guo de xiao xiang</span></p>
      <p begin="03:54.670" end="03:58.460" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L41"><span begin="03:54.670" end="03:54.980">我</span><span begin="03:54.980" end="03:55.360">依</span><span begin="03:55.360" end="03:55.670">然</span><span begin="03:55.700" end="03:56.060">记</span><span begin="03:56.090" end="03:56.310">得</span> <span begin="03:56.800" end="03:56.970">年</span><span begin="03:56.970" end="03:57.070">少</span><span begin="03:57.140" end="03:57.310">初</span><span begin="03:57.310" end="03:57.480">吻</span><span begin="03:57.510" end="03:57.650">的</span><span begin="03:57.690" end="03:57.750">那</span><span begin="03:57.860" end="03:58.130">教</span><span begin="03:58.220" end="03:58.460">堂</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我依然記得 年少初吻的那教堂</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I still remember the church of our youthful first kiss</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">まだ覚えている 若き日の初吻のあの教会を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어릴 적 첫 키스를 했던 그 성당을 여전히 기억해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je me souviens encore de l'église de notre premier baiser de jeunesse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aún recuerdo la iglesia de nuestro primer beso de juventud</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich erinnere mich noch immer an jene Kirche unseres ersten Kusses in der Jugend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu ainda me lembro daquela igreja do nosso primeiro beijo na juventude</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я всё ещё помню ту церковь нашего первого юношеского поцелуя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ricordo ancora la chiesa del nostro primo bacio di gioventù</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">wo yi ran ji de nian shao chu wen de na jiao tang</span></p>
      <p begin="03:58.920" end="04:05.070" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L42"><span begin="03:58.920" end="03:59.360">还</span><span begin="03:59.360" end="03:59.740">有</span><span begin="03:59.740" end="03:59.850">一</span><span begin="04:00.010" end="04:00.340">起</span><span begin="04:00.430" end="04:00.780">画</span><span begin="04:00.780" end="04:00.990">爱</span><span begin="04:01.090" end="04:01.670">心</span> <span begin="04:02.230" end="04:02.540">的</span><span begin="04:02.610" end="04:02.910">那</span><span begin="04:02.960" end="04:03.180">道</span><span begin="04:03.270" end="04:05.070">墙</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">還有一起畫愛心 的那道牆</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">And the wall where we drew a heart together</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">そして一緒にハートを描いた あの壁のことも</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그리고 함께 하트를 그렸던 그 벽도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et de ce mur où nous avions dessiné un cœur ensemble</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y esa pared donde dibujamos un corazón juntos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und an jene Wand an der wir zusammen ein Herz malten</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E daquela parede onde desenhamos um coração juntos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И ту стену где мы вместе нарисовали сердце</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E quel muro dove abbiamo disegnato un cuore insieme</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">hai you yi qi hua ai xin de na dao qiang</span></p>
    </div>
  </body>
</tt>
